9d1bd3a9232bfaaba","tid":431473,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有就無咁多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10個人名都夠<br />\n<br />\n寫死部份中共高宮<br />\n有人以為政治清算&gt;先下手為強&gt;內戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會係共產完結既之後衍生出其他問題<br />\n<br />\n一部分人暴動之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9910f8985d87a6a3e9400b848329ad018f659c","tid":431473,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地想同澳門人比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難d囉,澳門人冇你地咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感謝澳門人提供笑話一則"},{"pid":"eb76106296be58bb334db90efdf96e896b8aa48e","tid":431473,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地想同澳門人比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難d囉,澳門人冇你地咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23條都唔出嚟反抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難想像到香港人低賤啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31ebd815ca79b5c8b6b65e7074b69164b5a69f0","tid":431473,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f38af887a05f467846a16a1957974e134dc10b1b","tid":431473,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地想同澳門人比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難d囉,澳門人冇你地咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23條都唔出嚟反抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難想像到香港人低賤啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地又點反抗,一地兩檢有冇反抗,普教中有冇反抗,每日150有冇反抗,假難民有冇反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國民教育 23條 ，雖然唔係話多<br />\n總比你地年年拎住幾千蚊做狗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5591ffb90c3fd6cac530255e9e7e7f026528c88","tid":431473,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你想我報驚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n番去睇你老母比狗吊啦"},{"pid":"5bb79f3392fdb8ed50ed989b87c92138be674e68","tid":431473,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d82ccb95cab586befdf52dcafad7277d72cfe4b1","tid":431473,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地想同澳門人比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難d囉,澳門人冇你地咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23條都唔出嚟反抗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難想像到香港人低賤啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地又點反抗,一地兩檢有冇反抗,普教中有冇反抗,每日150有冇反抗,假難民有冇反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國民教育 23條 ，雖然唔係話多<br />\n總比你地年年拎住幾千蚊做狗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問你嗰d有冇反抗你又講其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟要我講幾多次你地先明其實真係唔關嗰幾千蚊事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔關錢事既話 請問關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直都冇追PO? 到而加仲有人討論緊你講果幾單野啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6683c03828b13e14d3c8136170de2d1162f3e0c1","tid":431473,"uid":50328,"like":0,"d